original_title: Mujibur sworn in as a National List MP
original_body_lines: Colombo, May 9 (Daily Mirror) - Mujibur Rahuman was sworn in as a National List MP before Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena a shortwhile ago.
Rahuman fills the vacancy created by the unseatimg of Diana Gamage who was declared to be ineligible to remain as an MP by the  Supreme Court.
